me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder2.prebuilt

Class TrajectoryFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder2.prebuilt.TrajectoryFactory

  • public class TrajectoryFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class used for working with trajectories. Instead of having to use so many constructors, these static methods allow you to convert single point (or multiple point) trajectory sequences, which can then be used by Pathfinder.
    Since:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    Colin Robertson
